window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A comprehensive guide to the foundations of Toltec wisdom, <i>Beyond Fear</i> is essential reading for fans of Don Miguel Ruizâ€™s <i>New York Times</i> best-selling book, <i>The Four Agreements</i>, which has sold over 8 million copies and has been translated into 46 languages worldwide. </p> <p>Providing instruction in the basic elements of the Toltec spiritual practice, this collection of ceremonies, wisdom, and prophecies empowers readers to shed their fears, judgments, and guilt - an essential step before practicing the Four Agreements.</p>"; 
